  <brief_title>Rituximab in Treating Patients With Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma or Hodgkin's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of C2B8 in Patients With Asymptomatic CD20+ B-Cell Follicular Small Cleaved Low-Grade Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma or Relapsed CD20+ Hodgkin's Disease</official_title>
